Bournemouth Crown Court heard Hampton, who was already banned from driving, told his wife, his employers, a car garage and the police his £40,000 Volvo had struck a deer.

Hampton paid £4,300 for the damage to the front of his vehicle to be hastily repaired, a jury was told.

The court heard Hampton struck Jade's scooter as he drove along the A31 in Ringwood, Hampshire, on February 24.

